            <h2>SIGA</h2>
            <div class="row">September 2022 -> Present</div>
            <p>At SIGA i first started working as a Trainee. As a Trainee i contributed in 3 different Teams, where i
                stayed around 6 Months. In this time i was introduced,
                to how the Team works, what their responsibility is and naturally helped them to fulfill those
